import {BrowserRouter as Router,Routes,Route} from "react-router-dom"



function Routing() {
  return (
    <>
    <Router>
        <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={<Questionaries/>} />
       <Route path="/Task" element={<Task/>} />
      
        </Routes>
    
    
    </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default Routing
